---
title: White Christmas Chocolate Cheesecake Pots with Salted Caramel and Pistachios
description: Something sweet for afters! This indulgent festive dessert combines layers of crunchy speculoos biscuit crumb, white chocolate cheesecake filling and smooth salted caramel. A final sprinkling of chopped pistachios make it a white Christmas delight.
